channel.description: I will stop making posts if people will just answer me i know im annoyin but i just have one prooblem i will explain... Whenever i open up my client (happens with other people too) and when i am playing on my server, i can type messages and it has normal speed when i type and the npc's dont lag, everything has no lag except when i click somewhere it takes like 5 seconds to do whatever action i clicked on sometimes even longer! so if you had that problem and fixed it please help my computer is not slow it's just that one problem please help this will be my last post about this problem! my msn is t.wall92@live.com add if you need!
